from theodore g benjamin subject re radio station in messge on mon apr greania steve greania write i do not have cable and on the night the cap do play i would like to tune in other game do anyone have a list of the radio station which broadcast the game for the nhl team here be the one i can remember offhand kdka am pittsburgh penguin wabc am new jersey devil wbbm am chicago blackhawk wjm am detroit redwing kmox am st loui blue are the flyer on that all i can think of ted benjamin go card go cav tedb go blue go vol go brown a sig can cramp one art 